Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:01.41,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,In my time of being an anime fan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:04.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I've seen this medium grow and evolved beyond my wildest dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:08.01,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Being an anime fan in 2018 is not only accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:12.31,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but it is exciting with countless shows to choose from, communities to get involved with
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:16.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and an industry that is getting the growth we always thought it deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.89,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The landscape is becoming something unrecognizable from when I first entered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And I am undoubtedly happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But there have been some things I have been nagging me for the longest time about this modern landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:30.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,A shadow that's been looming over that I can't help but notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And it's not something straightforward and obvious to point out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So I'm not really sure where I should begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a humble bounty hunter man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.76,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So how about I start right here with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,which sorry to break the immersion of having nice aesthetic anime clips as opposed to my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.31,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but to probably get my point across,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:54.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:56.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And it starts right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:57.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,In that shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:15.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,These are VHS tapes recordings of {\i1}Pokemon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.31,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,back when they first aired on {\i1}ITV{\i0} .
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:22.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And it is the birth of my anime fandom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:30.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I, like many others, first got their exposure to anime through {\i1}Pokemon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:34.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,which wasn't so weird considering how much of a worldwide sensation it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What was weird was that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:40.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I was the only one still watching it way after the craze had died out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:45.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And afterwards I would obsessively try to look for every other show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.91,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that had the same similar art style.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:51.05,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because I was the only one who liked this kind of show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:53.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And that's continued to my teenage years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:57.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where I would discover what anime was thanks to the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.49,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Now I knew nobody who liked anime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:03.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and even those of us on the Internet were in really small communities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:07.05,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And this would transition to my first DVD collection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,which actually consists mostly of bootlegs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:14.79,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,before I realized that {\i1}eBay{\i0} was not a licensed seller of anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:18.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Now a lot of these first buyers came from this standardized list of shows
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:22.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that would be constantly recommended by these small communities you'd find online.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:25.16,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Now that weren't a lot of us but as a newbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,these were the shows you had to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because these were {\i1}the classics{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Back in the day, anime fans had this unwritten rite of passage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:40.44,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,you'd have to go through before you could pass yourself off as a {\i1}Real Anime Fan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.69,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cowboy Bebop{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:42.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akira{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fullmetal Alchemist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.54,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And when you wanted to take on the final boss,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,you take a deep breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.11,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,put on your big boy pants
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:55.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and dive into the cluster fuck that was {\i1}Evangelion{\i0} discussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:59.54,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Well I'm glad a lot of this mentality of real anime fans is past now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.98,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,with a lot of the elitism it bred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,These were the shows everyone watch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:07.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,because they were the shows that were talked about no matter what year you got into anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.29,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And that's because of what the landscape was like back then as a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Being a fan then meant that you were a part of this niche community
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.83,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where all our common grounds was that we'd liked anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:20.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Cuz finding another person who did was a rare enough thing back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.76,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And these shows were typically some of the best and known stuff we had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.07,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,in the limited availability we were given.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We were limited by what licensing companies would choose to bring over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.59,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or what fans subbers would choose to sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:36.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Everything certainly wasn't readily available or instantly transferred over from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:37.91,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Legal or otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.06,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And because of this our approach to watching anime was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:45.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Choice was limited so people would invest time into finding a great anime for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Anime reviews held way more power than they do now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:51.87,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,because there was a higher level of commitment when choosing to watch a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.37,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,You didn't want to waste money on a show you didn't like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:59.27,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and even having torrents was less accessible than the one-click instant streaming accessibility of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.97,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So he meant way more when he found a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.52,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The shows were what defines the anime fandom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.04,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,along with the weirdness and eccentricities we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:11.39,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Being an anime fan felt like you were in this weird club separate from other communities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Something you couldn't find anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.21,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,In fact one of the biggest things that stops the fandom from growing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.83,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,was just how exclusive it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:23.19,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Yes anime fans were weird but that's the commonality we shared as a community.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:25.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And while certainly not everything was positive,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,things were definitely simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.46,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So if that's the way things were like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,what's changed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Today anime has changed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:45.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Well anime shows themselves have arguably remained the same for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But the landscape itself is undoubtedly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.61,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the biggest change that killed off the idea of {\i1}the classics{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Seasonal anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:55.98,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Seasonal anime or should I say current anime
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,has taken over the viewing habits of the modern anime fandom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.66,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,even if you're not following weekly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's about the shows that have aired in the last few months
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.67,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and the cycle of what is and isn't current now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.73,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is like three fucking days after a show ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:08.76,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Being part of the community
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:12.45,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,these are the shows you need to keep up with to be a part of the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.23,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's an ongoing cycle that just becomes our viewing habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.11,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The idea of the standardized list of classic anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:21.66,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,everyone watches to keep up with the current consensus of the fandom is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:25.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Before I felt like the entire timeline of anime was always up for grabs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,for newbies you had your rough starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Go do your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Also don't forget your history lesson here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.41,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Now it's about what's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.38,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.37,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Let's give everything a fucking try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.26,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What's an anime that seems like he could go somewhere after three episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What? It turns out the show sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Oh you fucking idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Why would you waste your time like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Ok, this time it definitely won't happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,As creatures of habit we are stuck in this endless cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.24,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And as constitutive as it sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:57.10,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,the important thing isn't about finding those killer shows you haven't seen yet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and would really appreciate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Our big motivator to watch shows now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.11,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is becoming part of a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Having our water cooler discussions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:09.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,we can have multiple shows we are simply content with as long as we get to discuss it with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:12.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And the thing is mentality in part started from something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.47,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that initially looked like a massive upside
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.84,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and that is that there is so much fucking anime coming out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And it only keeps increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:24.03,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago we celebrated the innovation of streaming companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:27.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,They gave us official anime simulcast with the same day release of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.23,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Five years ago you could just about keep up with all the shows worth watching
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,while occasionally discovering something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:38.47,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Today you better be jacked into the {\i1}Matrix{\i0} directly absorbing the anime into your 300 IQ brain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:41.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,because no sane fan can keep up with everything coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.89,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I can't even keep up with all the anime coming out now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and it's my fucking job to watch anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.09,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,You might as well rename your plan to watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Anime is such a wide world with so much variety in history
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.30,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,filled with amazing shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But when we're absolutely overwhelmed for the choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:06:59.58,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,what do we watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.92,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We watch what's right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We watch what we heard being discussed by our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.11,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,You log in to the front page of my streaming platforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,legal or otherwise and you're hit in the face with simulcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.53,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,new seasonal episodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.89,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,currently airing shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,If you're a casual viewer searching for something new
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or even if you just want a new show
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but don't know what you're in the mood for,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.69,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where are you even supposed to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Okay did I miss anything from last season.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:24.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Let me see the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.84,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Okay, what about two seasons, last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.47,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Okay I think I have enough now to last me through two nuclear winters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Everything is available.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:33.66,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Everything is abundant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:37.86,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But because of this, we're ironically more limited than we used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But really as much as some people would take this as,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.75,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, look at this idiot complaining about too much anime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.59,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hahahaha{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:47.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What I wanted to get out is that this is just a product of what the medium has become
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.76,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and how our attitude towards media has changed in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:51.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So let me ask you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.87,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What makes anime special
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:57.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,in this modern media landscape of mass consumption abundance of choice
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.64,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and mainstream nerd culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:04.44,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,As time goes on the answer becomes increasingly nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.59,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I think the {\u1}sense Minh{\u0} truly hit me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.27,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,when I started hearing from several different people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.55,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,how they would watch anime at 1.25 or 1.5 speed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.47,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,if they just wanted to get through a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And hearing that just blew my fuckin mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The fact that we the viewer could treat our entertainment as a commodity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:22.98,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that we try to consume and process as fast as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm talking to you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.76,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Stop watching this video 1.5 speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.43,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to make a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.44,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But the reality is anime is just another form of media
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:34.35,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that we consume in this modern age of digital consumption and we consume a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Anime doesn't only have to compete with other anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.90,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It has to compete with games, movies, YouTube,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.54,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,some fucking idiot starting drama on Twitter again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:46.38,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We are living in an age where time is limited and choice is abundant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:50.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Our most limiting resource when it comes to our entertainment now is no longer our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:51.98,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.47,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:58.12,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And media outlets have become very very good at capitalizing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.81,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,There's no longer that stop signal you used to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Netflix{\i0} tells you you don't even need to care about the end credits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:07.39,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The next recommended YouTube video is auto-played by default.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.96,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Your timeline is a bottomless pit you can scroll endlessly down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.41,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And as a side effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.58,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,our attention span have become incrementally shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,How many of you have sometimes looked at 20-minute anime episode of thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:20.19,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow 20 minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.58,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a pretty big commitment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'll watch it after this short 6-minute YouTube video.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:25.53,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh fuck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:28.24,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Even with shows in a modern day we find amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:33.93,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It feels like there's very little chance it'll even be thought about five, three, even one year later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.50,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because it just gets swallowed up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.91,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,as being another show in the endless pit of media we consume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:47.44,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Resume Viewing.x6
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:52.27,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The reality is anime isn't as distinct as it used to be in the grand scheme of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.81,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,As it has become a more widely accepted medium of entertainment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:59.53,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that exclusivity of the anime fandom is also disappearing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,for the better in my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:05.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But going with it is the uniqueness of being an anime fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,In the same way no one really says they're just a straight up gaming fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:13.90,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Saying you're an anime fan nowadays feels less like you're a part of a niche tight community.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.79,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But more like you're a part of a general movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.97,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Cuz it could mean a load of different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Do you only watch {\i1}Shounen{\i0}, {\i1}Mecha{\i0}, {\i1}Idols{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.69,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Are you a casual viewer, cosplayer, artist, animator, data entry clerk for your watch list?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.45,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Anime fan means a whole different thing than he used to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.63,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and in an age where we could have something in common
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:35.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,with people like {\i1}Michael B. Jordan{\i0} and {\i1}John Boyega{\i0} and {\i1}Kim{\s1} fucking {\s0}Kardashian{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:38.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The biggest difference about being an anime fan today is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.43,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's not just about the anime shows anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:45.05,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's about the anime culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.78,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The weirdness and eccentricities have become normalized and accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The anime aesthetic is becoming widely spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's about that social aspect that was never as prevalent before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's about being part of the conversation and that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But I think because of this we need to recognize that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:02.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,our approach to the medium shouldn't be the same as it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because I think for a lot of us it still is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:07.36,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Anime is no longer that same niche little community.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.05,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's no longer any guarantee that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:13.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,2 people who call themselves anime fans will have the same kind of common ground they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:17.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because we are becoming too big to simply segregate into one group
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.92,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and I think it's also time we drop the notion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.96,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that we should try to keep up with everything anime has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It used to be that as an anime fan you could be aware of every new show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.15,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Everything worth talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.19,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Everything that the community was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.84,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But I think we've reached the breaking point
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where it's reasonable to feel pressure to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:38.26,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,In the same way that no one feels pressure to watch every movie that comes out worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:42.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Nor do people feel pressured to keep up with every game that comes out on {\i1}Steam{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.96,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,A lot of the discussion around piracy recently have been around the inconvenience of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,so many different shows being distributed on different platforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.21,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But with too many shows to choose from the starts becoming less of an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:56.01,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What's likely to happen is that the casual consumer will end up just filing shows
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:12:00.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that interest them on their platform or preference like most people do with their entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.63,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It won't become about keeping up with the community and the fandom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:06.73,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It becomes about what's marketed the most and what's most visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.92,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It becomes about who can best generate hype for their products.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:14.53,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It becomes as you guessed it like every other industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.72,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because that's exactly what's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:20.05,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The industry in the West is now dominated by massive corporations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:25.03,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or smaller anime focus brands that are now owned by massive corporations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's no longer just that same fan-run industry used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.11,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and with the money being invested into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:33.21,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,the companies have to realize that the audiences are starting to treat them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:37.26,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,with the same corporate standards and expectations that they do for other industries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.39,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What I want to end on is just hammering down
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:43.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that this isn't meant to be a complaint about how things have gotten worse or that the old days were better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.26,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I love anime today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.44,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I love what it has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:49.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And the friends and opportunities I've gotten because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:53.24,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But as exactly because of this then I feel the medium is reaching a crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:57.64,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It might not be on the same level as things like gaming or {\i1}Marvel{\i0} movies just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.50,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But the medium I grew up loving has also grown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.70,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and it's coming to the time where I have to change the way I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:08.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,when it was something small and niche and well, special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Things aren't as simple as they used to be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:13.78,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and we should keep this in mind as we transition into something bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:17.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and anime finds a space in the modern entertainment landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.16,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Anime has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The community has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The industry has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:27.93,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And I think the time has come that the way we treat it, has to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:01.41,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在我成为动画粉丝的这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:04.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这种媒介的成长与演变远超我的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:08.01,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在{\s1}8102年{\s0} 2018年成为一个动画粉不仅能被公众接受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:12.31,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而且还很刺激 有无数的动画可以选择观看 有无数的社区可以参与
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:16.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,还有一个我们觉得会一直蒸蒸日上的业界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.89,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,形势与我刚入坑的时候产生了极大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,毋庸置疑 我对此感到很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是一提到现在的动画 有些东西总在困扰着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:30.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我察觉到了一片阴影的缓慢出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:33.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,想指明它并不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,所以我也不知道该从何讲起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}不过是个低调的赏金猎人{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.76,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不如在这里和我一起开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:49.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,啊真是不好意思打扰了各位享受艺术动画剪辑中的美好沉浸感而要直面我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.31,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,为了较好地传达我的观点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我想讲个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:54.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:56.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,从这里开始的我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:57.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就在那个棚屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:15.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些是{\i1}宝可梦{\i0} 的VHS录像带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.31,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,可以追溯到它在{\i1}ITV{\i0} 刚上映的那段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:22.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这也是我入坑动画的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:30.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我和很多其他人一样 通过{\i1}宝可梦{\i0} 第一次接触到了动画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:34.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,考虑到{\i1}宝可梦{\i0} 在世界上传播的广泛性 这并不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:36.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,奇怪的则是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:40.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我是唯一一个在热潮过后还在看它的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:45.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,之后我痴迷于寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.91,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,每一个和{\i1}宝可梦 {\i0}有着类似风格的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:51.05,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为我是唯一一个喜欢动画的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:53.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这在我青少年时期得以延续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:57.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,多谢互联网的存在 那时我真正弄清楚了日本动画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.49,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在我知道那时基本没人喜欢动画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:03.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就算是网上的动画粉丝团体也只是处在一个极小的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:07.05,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,直到我买第一套DVD合集的时候发生了转变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,其实包含了许多盗版碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:14.79,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那时我还不知道{\i1}eBay{\i0} 没有卖动画类产品的授权
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:18.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在许多买碟新人都来自这个标准化动画清单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:22.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而这些清单往往是被那些网上的小社区所推荐的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:25.16,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然这不是我们中的大多数 但是作为一个新人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些动画你必须要看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为这些动画是{\i1}经典{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:36.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那时候 动画粉丝有个不成文的认证仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:40.44,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你必须得证明你是{\i1}真动画粉{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.69,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}星际牛仔{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:42.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}阿基拉{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}钢之炼金术师{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.54,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而当你要对付最终Boss的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你深呼吸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.11,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,穿上你那宽松的男孩短裤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:55.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,然后逃入人群中 这就是我们所说的{\i1}EVA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:59.54,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然我很高兴这些辣鸡死宅心态现在已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.98,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,尽管这影响了不少大佬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些确实是那些年每个人都看过的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:07.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在以前 不管你是哪年入坑 你都会讨论这些动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.29,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这是因为在那个时候 整个动画粉丝圈的形势 只是作为粉丝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.56,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,成为粉丝意味着你成为了这个小众社区的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:16.83,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而那时我们聚集到一起共同的理由不过是我们喜欢动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:20.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那时确实很难找到另一个同好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:23.76,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,一般而言这些动画都是我们那时所知的最好最知名的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.07,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,要么其他更好的动画也是因为供应限制而无法看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:29.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们受限于那些代理公司的选择引进的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.59,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者是字幕组选择制作字幕的那些动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:36.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,并不是所有的日本动画能马上从日本传过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:37.91,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,无论合法与否
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:41.06,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因此我们看动画的方法因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:45.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,选择是有限的 因此人们需要花费时间来为自己找好动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画评论者比现在所拥有的影响力大得多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:51.87,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为以前看动画需要更多的付出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.37,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你不想在你不喜欢看的动画上花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:59.27,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就算是通过种子下载也没有现在这种一键立刻播放的视频流服务方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.97,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,所以找好动画的意义比现在大得多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.52,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些好动画定义了动画粉丝文化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.04,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,与此同时还有那些古怪的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:11.39,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,成为一个动画粉丝就像是你在一个与世隔绝的团体之内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:13.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,有些东西你在别的地方是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.21,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,事实上 阻止这个粉丝团体继续扩张的一大原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.83,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就是它有多么独特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:23.19,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,没错 动画粉丝是有些奇怪 但这是我们作为一个团体所共有的特性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:25.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然不是所有的东西都是正面的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:28.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,总体上来讲都比现在要更纯粹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.46,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,以前是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那现在又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在的动画确实有很大改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:45.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然 动画大多数部分仍饱受争议地保持着原来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:47.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是整个形势却毋庸置疑地发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.61,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们从{\i1}经典{\i0} 理念的消亡这个最大的改变开始讲起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,季度番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:55.98,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,季度番或者说是现在在播的番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,控制了现代动画粉丝圈的观看习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.66,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就算你不是每周都追着看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,包括那些过去几个月内播出的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.67,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,可能这个播出周期并不涵盖现在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.73,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,可能是完结后的三天这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:08.76,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,成为社区的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:12.45,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,看完这些动画你才能跟得上话题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.23,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这个不断发展的周期成为了我们的观看习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.11,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,标准化经典番剧观看清单的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:21.66,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那些让大家看完之后达成共识的粉丝圈已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:25.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在我感觉整个动画的时间表都是用来吸引眼球之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,对于新人来讲 你的入门并不会那么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:30.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,回去做作业去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,也别忘了这些历史课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.41,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在来讲讲什么比较流行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.38,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,什么不流行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.37,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我来举个例
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.26,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,三集定律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,什么 是个烂番
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,吔屎啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你怎么可以花时间看烂番
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:48.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然 这次这些东西绝不会在我身上发生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,作为习惯的生物 我们会卡在这个无尽的循环中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.24,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,基本上来讲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:57.10,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,重要的不是找那些没看过的好看的动画来看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,并对此真心感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在我们看番的最大动机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.11,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,是参与到话题中来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,参与我们冷静的讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:09.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,只要是那些我们能和别人讨论的动画 就能让人满意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:12.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而这种糟糕的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.47,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,发展自某种一开始看起来是个蛮积极的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.84,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但也就仅此而已了 现在有太多辣鸡动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.56,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,还在不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:24.03,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,十年前我们在庆祝视频流公司的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:27.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,它们给我们带来了和日本官方相同的连载动画发布时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.23,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,五年前你能恰好跟上所有值得观看的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,与此同时偶尔发现一些新系列
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:38.47,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,今天你最好直接脑后插管通过你那智商300的大脑连接{\i1}母体{\i0} 并吸收动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:41.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为没有那个疯狂的粉丝可以跟上所有发布出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.89,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我都不能跟上所有现在发布出来的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:46.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,尽管我的工作是看动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.09,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你也许会变更你的观看计划来观看这些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,日本动画历史上涉及的种类如此之广泛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.30,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,充满了神作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是当我们选择太多的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:06:59.58,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们该看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:01.92,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们看正前方出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们看朋友们讨论的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.11,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你登进视频流播放平台的首页
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不管合法与否 你都会看到一堆连载中的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.53,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,季度新番
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.89,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在正播出的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果你只是想随便找点动画来看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,亦或是想找个新动画来看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是不知道自己喜欢哪种类型的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.69,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你该从何开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,好的 让我看看上个季度我错过了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:24.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,让我看一下清单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.84,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,好的 再多看两个季度 或者是去年的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,两年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.47,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,好的 光看这些我甚至可以熬过两个核冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:33.66,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,种类都很丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:37.86,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但也因此 讽刺地是 我们比过去受到的限制更多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是会有些人这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:42.75,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嘿 这有个喷子居然在喷动画太多{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.59,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}哈哈哈哈{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:47.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这是动画这个媒介变化后的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.76,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而大体上 我们看媒体的方式也发生了改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:51.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,所以如果我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:53.87,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在这个大众消费丰富的现代媒体形势中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:57.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,是什么让日本动画独树一帜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.64,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然也包括主流nerd文化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:04.44,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,随着时间的推移 这个回答逐渐变得没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.59,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我认为快进党的这个说法真的冲击到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.27,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当我听说好几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.55,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,都是1.25倍速或者1.5倍速看动画的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.47,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当他们只是想看完动画的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,听到这个真的让我震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,事实上观众可以把娱乐当作一种快消品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:22.98,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就是一种消费得越快越好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我在说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.76,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,别用1.5倍速看这个视频了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.43,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我正在发表看法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.44,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过事实上动画也就是一种传播媒介而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:34.35,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,只是我们在这个现代数字消费时代消费的很多东西中的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画不只是和别的动画竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.90,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,它也需要和游戏 电影 油管
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:42.54,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,甚至一些推特上的戏精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:46.38,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们生活在一个时间有限但选择过于丰富的年代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:50.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在在娱乐上面 受限的资源并不是我们的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:51.98,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而是我们的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.47,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,是我们的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:58.12,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而媒体公司非常擅长在这个上面压榨价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.81,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不再有以前那样的停止符号了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Netflix{\i0} 甚至告诉你 你不需要关注片尾制作名单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:07.39,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,下一个油管推荐视频甚至是默认自动播放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:10.96,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你的时间线就是个无底洞 你可以无尽地往下滚动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.41,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而副作用是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.58,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们关注一件事的时间变得越来越短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你们有多少人看20分钟动画的时候会想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:20.19,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}哇 20分钟呢{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.58,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}这是个很大的投入{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}也许我应该先看这个6分钟的油管短视频{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:25.53,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}我去{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:28.24,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,甚至是现在我们觉得很好看的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:33.93,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,感觉5年后 3年后 甚至1年后都不太可能想得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.50,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为它被新事物淹没了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.91,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,成为有一个我们消费过然后丢在无底洞里的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:47.44,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,继续观看x6
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:52.27,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,事实上动画并没有以前那么独树一帜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:55.81,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正如它变成了一种广为人知的娱乐媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:59.53,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画粉丝圈的独特性也在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:05.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是一同消失的也包括成为动画粉丝的独特性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就像是没有谁会直接说他是一个游戏粉丝一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:13.90,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\fs50}现在说自己是个动画粉丝 并不会像以前那样感觉自己处在一个关系密切的小众社区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.79,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是感觉更像是处在一个大众活动当中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.97,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为这意味着许多不同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你只看{\i1}少年{\i0} {\i1}机甲{\i0} {\i1}偶像{\i0} 类动画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:25.69,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\fs43}你做出这个动画观看列表 是因为你是漫不经心的观众 角色扮演 艺术家 动画制作者还是数据录入员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.45,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画粉丝这个词和以前大不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.63,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,以前我们能有一些共同点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:35.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,哪怕是{\i1}Michael B. Jordan{\i0}和{\i1}John Boyega{\i0}还有{\i1}KimKardashian{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:38.56,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在的动画粉丝的巨大不同就在于此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:42.43,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是关于动画作品本身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:45.05,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,还关于动画文化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.78,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,稀奇古怪的东西被正常化并被接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画的艺术性被广泛地传播了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在社会上 动画从未有现在这样如此流行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:56.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在俨然成为了讨论的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正因如此 我们需要承认
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:02.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在我们观看媒体的方式和过去不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就算是对于我们动画粉丝而言也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:07.36,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,日本动画不再是以前那个小众社区了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.05,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不能保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:13.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,两个动画粉丝之间就像以前一样还有相同的兴趣爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:17.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为动画粉丝团体变得太过庞大 无法再按以前那样分成一个类别
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.92,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在是总结的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.96,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们应该尽力跟上动画所提供的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:26.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,过去一个动画粉丝可以知晓每个新推出的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.15,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,每件事都值得讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.19,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正如整个社区所做的事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:31.84,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是我认为现在到达了一个转折点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,有足够的理由不再跟上动画的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:38.26,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,同理 没有谁应该为不能看到所有推出的电影而感到压力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:42.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者是不能玩到所有{\i1}Steam{\i0} 上推出的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.96,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,盗版领域人们最近总在讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这么多动画在不同的平台发布带来的不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:52.21,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是因为可选择的动画太多了 这反而不再是大问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:56.01,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,有可能发生的是 观众们只是把他们认为有趣的动画归档起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:12:00.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就像人们对待他们的娱乐活动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.63,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,日本动画不再是和社区或者粉丝圈保持一致步调
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:06.73,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而是关于哪些东西是卖得最好的 是最引人注目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.92,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,是关于那些最会炒作的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:14.53,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就像任何其他行业一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.72,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正如现在所发生的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:20.05,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,西方世界的行业现在被大集团所把控
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:25.03,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者是一些小动画品牌被大集团控制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:28.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不再是以前那个粉丝驱动的行业了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.11,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,随着金钱的投入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:33.21,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,公司企业会意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:37.26,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,观众会像其他行业那样用相同的标准和期待来对待他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.39,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我想像这样一锤定音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:43.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就是这个视频并不是为了抱怨现在变得更差而以前更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.26,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我现在还喜欢着动画
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.44,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢它变化后的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:49.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,同样也喜欢因为动画而结识的朋友和机遇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:53.24,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正因如此我觉得这个行业正面临一个转折点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:57.64,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,可能并不会达到游戏或者{\i1}漫威{\i0} 电影那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.50,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,可是我成长时期喜欢的那个动画产业现在也长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.70,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在到了那个我需要改变我的看法的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:08.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画行业不再是以前那样小而独特
